# Nothing needed here — the NICE_VIEW_WIDGET_STATUS symbol is suppressed via
# an explicit OVERLAY_CONFIG conf file (disable_nice_view_widget.conf) that is
# passed through build.yaml cmake-args.  An explicit conf-file assignment beats
# the `imply NICE_VIEW_WIDGET_STATUS` in nice_view/Kconfig.defconfig, whereas
# a Kconfig `default n` here would be overridden by the imply.
